Class NondeterministicModuleException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • net.sourceforge.waters.model.base.WatersException

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class NondeterministicModuleException
extends EvalException
    An exception thrown by the ModuleGraphCompiler to indicate that a graph compiles to a nondeterministic automaton although it is declared to be deterministic.
    Author:
    Robi Malik
